org.openmuc.jdlms

Class SnClassInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openmuc.jdlms.SnClassInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SnClassInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Interface class (IC) info used to enable the mapping between attribute or method ID and SN offset. This class is only applicable if SN referencing is used.
    See Also:
    ConnectionBuilder.setSnClassInfo(java.util.Collection), SnObjectInfo, Serialized Form
